# The object detector I Spy plays with: 14MB of wasm and weights, fetched by
# scripts/fetch-detector.sh, which pins every byte of it by SHA-256. Not in git,
# because it would sit in the history for ever and never change; baked into the
# image, because a game that phones a CDN mid-round is a game that stops working
# on the day the CDN does.
waiting_games/static/vendor/
